OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FGradually turning brighter
OL,6,Fwith warm sunny spells developing and
OL,7,Falso scattered afternoon showers,
OL,8,Fthese locally heavy with a low chance
OL,9,Fof thunder. Winds remaining generally
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,13,For sunny spells and a chance of
OL,14,Fshowers each day, these perhaps more
OL,15,Flikely Tuesday. Turning cooler, with
OL,16,Fovernight rural grass frost possible
OL,17,Fin sheltered spots. Winds mostly light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
